[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/overcalls"]
[Student "S"]
{NORTH has a 19 point balanced hand, including a stop in \Hs. 
He plans to double, then bid NT. (see Deal 9)

SOUTH has 10 points though, so he jumps to 2\S. 

In theory NORTH could now bid 2NT to continue the description of his hand, but he might as well 
go ahead and bid 3NT instead.}

